# Step 8 (2026-06-27) single-driver dry-run artifacts.
# The single-driver in experiments/run/run_benchmark.py splits the
# merged <benchmark>_<variant>.yaml into a sibling <job_name>.job.yaml
# + <job_name>.method.yaml before invoking ``skillq paper run``. These
# are ephemeral; the merged YAMLs in experiments/configs/ are the
# committed source of truth. Don't check the split files in.
experiments/configs/*.job.yaml
experiments/configs/*.method.yaml

